  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to investigate whether preemptive medication with dexamethasone
      or etoricoxib provides better pain management and control than placebo following periodontal
      surgery.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
