  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  Patients presenting moderate or severe periodontitis after nonsurgical periodontal
             treatment with clinical signs of inflammation

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Pregnant

          -  Diabetes mellitus

          -  Heart diseases

          -  Allergic to components of the medications

          -  Risk of endocarditis
      </textblock>
    </criteria>
